=====================================================
Car Rental System – Low Level Design (LLD)
Amazon SDE-2 Interview Oriented
=====================================================

1. PROBLEM OVERVIEW
------------------
Design a Car Rental System that allows users to search, reserve, pick up,
and return cars across multiple cities and locations. The system must
prevent double booking, support extensible pricing strategies, and handle
concurrency correctly.

Scope:
- Multiple cities
- Multiple locations per city
- Each location owns its fleet of vehicles
- Cars are picked up and returned at the same location
- Only car rentals (future extensible to other vehicle types)

Out of Scope:
- Authentication / Authorization
- External payment gateway
- UI / APIs
- Cross-location drop-offs
- GPS tracking

