5. VEHICLE ABSTRACTION
---------------------

Interface: Vehicle
------------------
Attributes:
- vehicleId
- brand
- model
- fuelType
- transmissionType
- VehicleType
- VehicleStatus
- PricingStrategy pricingStrategy

Methods:
- getVehicleId()
- getVehicleType()
- getStatus()
- setStatus(VehicleStatus status)
- calculatePrice(startTime, endTime)

Concrete Implementations:
- Sedan
- SUV
- Hatchback
- LuxuryCar

Notes:
- Pricing is NOT hardcoded inside vehicle
- Vehicle delegates price calculation to PricingStrategy

-----------------------------------------------------

6. PRICING STRATEGY
------------------

Interface: PricingStrategy
--------------------------
Method:
- calculatePrice(startTime, endTime)

Concrete Implementations:
- HourlyPricingStrategy
- DailyPricingStrategy
- Future: SurgePricingStrategy, DiscountPricingStrategy

Design Choice:
- Strategy Pattern
- Allows pricing changes without modifying Vehicle or Reservation code

