7. RESERVATION
--------------

Class: Reservation
------------------
Attributes:
- reservationId
- User user
- Vehicle vehicle
- locationId
- startTime
- endTime
- ReservationStatus status
- Payment payment

Methods:
- confirmReservation()
- cancelReservation()
- completeReservation()

Rules:
- Reservation blocks vehicle for a given time window
- Cancellation allowed only before rental start time
- Once confirmed, vehicle cannot be reserved by others

